opendial.templates

Class RelationalTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.datastructs.Graph<Template,Template>
      • opendial.templates.RelationalTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Template>, Template

    public class RelationalTemplate
extends Graph<Template,Template>
implements Template
    Template for a relational structure. Both the node content and relations can be "templated" (i.e. underspecified). See the Graph class for more details on the string representation.
